          "id": "2c8dbb5c03db1e177212ecbd9096340798987185",
          "message": "chore(deps): update rust crate azure_core to v1.1.0 (#3463)\n\nThis PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| [azure_core](https://redirect.github.com/azure/azure-sdk-for-rust) |\nworkspace.dependencies | minor | `1.0.0` ŌåÆ `1.1.0` |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>azure/azure-sdk-for-rust (azure_core)</summary>\n\n###\n[`v1.1.0`](https://redirect.github.com/Azure/azure-sdk-for-rust/releases/tag/azure_core%401.1.0)\n\n[Compare\nSource](https://redirect.github.com/azure/azure-sdk-for-rust/compare/azure_core@1.0.0...azure_core@1.1.0)\n\n#### 1.1.0 (2026-07-09)\n\n##### Features Added\n\n- `Error` now captures a `std::backtrace::Backtrace` at construction\ntime and includes it in `Debug` output (e.g., `{:?}`) when\n`RUST_BACKTRACE=1` is set.\n\n##### Other Changes\n\n- Added `#[must_use]` to `AsyncRuntime` functions.\n- Added `#[must_use]` to `ItemIterator` (`Pager`) and `PageIterator`\ntypes.\n- Added `#[must_use]` to `Poller` type.\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Configuration\n\n­¤ōģ **Schedule**: (UTC)\n\n- Branch creation\n  - \"before 8am on Monday\"\n- Automerge\n  - At any time (no schedule defined)\n\n­¤Ü” **Automerge**: Disabled by config. Please merge this manually once you\nare satisfied.\n\nŌÖ╗ **Rebasing**: Whenever PR becomes conflicted, or you tick the\nrebase/retry checkbox.\n\n­¤öĢ **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update\nagain.\n\n---\n\n- [ ] <!-- rebase-check -->If you want to rebase/retry this PR, check\nthis box\n\n---\n\nThis PR was generated by [Mend Renovate](https://mend.io/renovate/).\nView the [repository job\nlog](https://developer.mend.io/github/open-telemetry/otel-arrow).\n\n<!--renovate-debug:eyJjcmVhdGVkSW5WZXIiOiI0My4yNTkuMiIsInVwZGF0ZWRJblZlciI6IjQzLjI1OS4yIiwidGFyZ2V0QnJhbmNoIjoibWFpbiIsImxhYmVscyI6WyJkZXBlbmRlbmNpZXMiXX0=-->\n\nCo-authored-by: renovate[bot] <29139614+renovate[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>",
