          "message": "chore(clickhouse-exporter): fix misleading password and TTL examples in docs (#3503)\n\nFollow-up to #3291.\n\n- README Quick Start: docker `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD=TODO-TEST` ŌåÆ `test` so\nit matches the sample config's fallback and the three-step flow works\nwith no extra env setup.\n- Doc-comments on `TableConfig.ttl` / `FinalTableConfig.ttl` and the\n`test_config_deserialization` fixture: `\"72h\"`/`\"12h\"` ŌåÆ `\"72\nHOUR\"`/`\"12 HOUR\"`, since `validate_ttl` requires a time-unit keyword.\n\nNo behavior change.",
